text: Desmiphoropsis mannerheimi is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Thomson in 1865. It is known from French Guiana.BioLib.cz - Desmiphoropsis mannerheimi. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Compsosomatini Category:Beetles described in 1865
title: Desmiphoropsis mannerheimi
